_sText:
A 6v8 hostage rescue map. The terrorists told the hostages not to move from their position because otherwise they will be killed. But is it really true using the Counter-Terrorists force?

Counter-Terrorists Objective (CT's): Rescue 5 hostages or kill all terrorists (T's).

Terrorists Objective (T's): Prevent the hostages from being rescued or kill all Counter-Terrorists (CT's).
